OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSri Lanka central bank lays
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fout extent of crisis       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sri Lanka's central bank has laid out  
OL,6, the extent of the country's worst      
OL,7, economic crisis in more than 70 years. 
OL,9,FIn its annual report, the bank outlined
OL,10,Fhow last year wages failed to keep up  
OL,11,Fwith the soaring cost of everything    
OL,12,Ffrom food to fuel.                     
OL,14,F"Several inherent weaknesses" and      
OL,15,F"policy lapses" helped to trigger the  
OL,16,Fsevere economic problems that engulfed 
OL,17,Fthe South Asian nation, the bank says. 
OL,19,FThe bank now expects the economy to    
OL,20,Freturn to growth next year.            
